locality: Parque Nal. Amboró. Río Saguayo. Bosque húmedo tropical.
Parque Nacional Amboro, 23 km S of Buena Vista, along Rio Chonta. Lowland tropical evergreen forest.

Parque Nacional Amboro, along Rio Saguayo, 1 km NE of entrance into first Andean foothills. Tropical evergreen forest on low hills of unconsolidated sediments and edges along river. Guadua angustifolia, Tipuana tipu.
